des:
Start your day with an list of inspirational quotes of Param Pujya Dada Bhagwan. 

Param Pujya Dada Bhagwan is a Gnani Purush (Spiritual Master) and the founder of Akram Vignan, who is not only Self-Realized, but also has the spiritual power to enlighten others. 

When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
